description	"Selkath Spy

^2Weaponry:
- Vibro Knife
-- Yellow / Blue Styles
-- Saber Defense (1)
- Disruptor Pistol (2)
-- Based on Bryar Pistol
-- Sets Targets On Fire
-- Disintegrates Targets On Death
-- 15% Slower Movement While Held
- 1 Concussion Grenade
- 1 Sonic Detonator
- 3 Trip Mines

^6Inventory:
- Stealth Field Generator

^8Attributes:
- Immune to Sense
- Stamina (2)
- Reinforcements (1)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]
- Grappling Hook (2)

Selkath spies, engaged in concealed partnership with the Republic, overcame their initial aversion to assassination, employing all available methods during the Ahto City uprising to counter the Sith assault."